testimonials.text: Sanel is an excelent team player and one of the important team members on VG/VI project, with a potential to become a team leader in the near future. He is reliable employee, commited to his work. Always delivering what is expecting of him with minimal supervision.

I am grateful to Sanel for helping me out when I was having trouble with a Selenium web scraper. He immediately identified the problem and solved it. He also sent me remarkably clearly and detailed messages. I look forward to working with him again in the future.
